snippet.title: Deus Ex - Lay D Denton Project 1.0 Announcement
snippet.description:
Version 1.0 is live. LDDP is feature complete and Female JC can be played from beginning to end.

The Lay D Denton project is an effort to provide a FULL female JC Denton experience. Features include a complete female JC voiceover, female JC model, modified pronouns and gender references, additional minor characters, and scene changes appropriate to a female JC.

Discord: https://discord.gg/MdW7KW8jFr
Install Instructions: https://docs.google.com/document/d/13ed4o3Ap7ONOW4vrhpd1gaAOImiGFda9/
ModDB: https://www.moddb.com/mods/the-lay-d-denton-project/downloads/lay-d-denton-project-1-0

Credits:
Karen Rohan -- JC Denton, Modified Cover Art and Additional Art Assets
Chris Rohan -- Vocal Director, Additional Characters
Kyle "Mr. Poke" Peach -- Maps & Programming
WCCC -- Additional Programming
Bogie -- Female JC Character Model

Trailer music cover composed by Mairiba and used with permission
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmmOgYY7oX2tWoHPiS4TGOg
